original_title: SoundStage Presents: Robert Plant And The Strange Sensation
overview: Soundstage: Robert Plant and the Strange Sensation is the first live DVD by Robert Plant and the Strange Sensation, featuring a performance filmed for the Soundstage television series in Chicago on September 16, 2005, in addition to bonus features from prior to the founding of the Strange Sensation  1.	"No Quarter"  - 2.	"Shine It All Around" - 3.	"Black Dog" - 4.	"Freedom Fries"  5.	"Four Sticks" - 6.	"Tin Pan Valley" - 7.	"Gallow's Pole" - 8.	"The Enchanter" - 9.	"Whole Lotta Love"
title: SoundStage Presents: Robert Plant And The Strange Sensation
